<item>
            <title>[FLINK-8798] Make commons-logging a parent-first pattern</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-8798</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Apache &lt;tt&gt;commons-logging&lt;/tt&gt; framework does not play well with child-first classloading.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We need to make this a parent-first pattern.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a matter of fact, other frameworks that use inverted classloading (JBoss, Tomcat) use force this library to be always parent-first as well.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
